n><span class=\"v40_25_18\"><sup id=\"Matt.25.18\" class=\"v40_25_18\">18</sup><span class=\"wj\">But he who had received the one talent went and </span><span class=\"wj\">dug in the ground and hid his master\u2019s money.</span></span><span class=\"v40_25_19\"><sup id=\"Matt.25.19\" class=\"v40_25_19\">19</sup><span class=\"wj\">Now </span><span class=\"wj\">after a long time the master of those servants came and </span><span class=\"wj\">settled accounts with them.</span></span><span class=\"v40_25_20\"><sup id=\"Matt.25.20\" class=\"v40_25_20\">20</sup><span class=\"wj\">And he who had received the five talents came forward, bringing five talents more, saying, \u2018Master, you delivered to me five talents; here I have made five talents more.\u2019</span></span><span class=\"v40_25_21\"><sup id=\"Matt.25.21\" class=\"v40_25_21\">21</sup><span class=\"wj\">His master said to him, \u2018Well done, good and </span><span class=\"wj\">faithful servant.</span><span class=\"wj\">You have been faithful over a little; </span><span class=\"wj\">I will set you over much. Enter into </span><span class=\"wj\">the joy of your master.\u2019</span></span><span class=\"v40_25_22\"><sup id=\"Matt.25.22\" class=\"v40_25_22\">22</sup><span class=\"wj\">And he also who had the two talents came forward, saying, \u2018Master, you delivered to me two talents; here I have made two talents more.\u2019</span></span><span class=\"v40_25_23\"><sup id=\"Matt.25.23\" class=\"v40_25_23\">23</sup><span class=\"wj\">His master said to him, \u2018Well done, good and faithful servant. You have been faithful over a little; I will set you over much. Enter into the joy of your master.\u2019</span></span><span class=\"v40_25_24\"><sup id=\"Matt.25.24\" class=\"v40_25_24\">24</sup><span class=\"wj\">He also who had received the one talent came forward, saying, \u2018Master, I knew you to be </span><span class=\"wj\">a hard man, reaping </span><span class=\"wj\">where you did not sow, and gathering where